Package blackboxTester.parser.ast

Interface Summary
RHS The right hand side of a rewrite rule
Term A class representing a term in the left or right hand sides of a rewrite rule abstract syntax tree.
Type An interface representing types of the parsed input.
 

Class Summary
DynamicType An abstract syntax tree representing a non-primitive type in the parsed input.
Equation An abstract syntax tree representing an Equation in the the parsed input.
Input Abstract syntax tree representing the overall input to the blackbox tester program.
Operation An operation in a rewrite rule
OpSpec An abstract syntax tree representing the operation specs in the parsed input.
PrimitiveType An abstract syntax tree representing a primitive type.
PrimitiveType.BooleanType Abstract syntax tree representing a boolean type in the parsed input.
PrimitiveType.CharacterType Abstract syntax tree representing a character type in the parsed input.
PrimitiveType.IntegerType Abstract syntax tree representing an integer type in the parsed input.
PrimitiveType.StringType Abstract syntax tree representing a string type in the parsed input.
RHSFalse A class representing the "#f" value in the right hand side of a rewrite rule.
RHSInteger A class representing an integer in the right hand side of a rewrite rule.
RHSOperation A class representing an operation on the right hand side of a rewrite equation.
RHSPrimitiveOperation A class representing primitive operations on the right hand side of a rewrite rule.
RHSTrue A class representing the "#f" value in the right hand side of a rewrite rule.
Signature An abstract syntax tree representing the signatures in the parsed input.
Variable A class representing a variable on either the right or left hand sides of a rewrite rule abstract syntax tree.
